---
title: Sesame Soy Baked Chicken Thighs with Stir-Fried Bulgogi Veg and Jasmine Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sesame Soy Baked Chicken Thighs in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
